	<section>
		<title>Documentation Updates</title>
		<body>
			<p>
			From Gentoo-2004.0 and all its pre-releases on, all single-document manuals are seen as
			deprecated. From this release on, the official documentation source is the Gentoo Handbook 
			that bundles all single-document manuals into a multi-document
